These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, water, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, musical, epic, time-travel, romance
There are 5 different nationalities: german, indian, polish, french, argentine
5 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, hamster, hedgehog, snake
 1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 7. the german is on the left of the polish##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the indian and the person watching romance movies##2
12. the french is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
13. the argentine is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | milk        | soy-milk | hot-chocolate     | water   | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | musical      | time-travel | romance   | fantasy    |
| Nationality   | french  | indian     | german | polish | argentine  |
| Pet           | cat | hamster      | snake     | hedgehog   | ferret     |

