.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, dancing, woodworking
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, punk, rock, trance, blues
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, pakistani, canadian, argentine, malaysian
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, airplane, tram, train, subway
 1. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the pakistani##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is between the italian and the fan of blues##2
 6. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the fan of indie is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the canadian is the fan of trance##1
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of punk##1
11. the canadian is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking | woodworking    | collecting  | drawing    |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | punk       | rock      | indie | trance        |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | pakistani     | italian    | argentine  | canadian     |
| Transport     | tram    | airplane | subway | train | motorbike |

