.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, video-games, skydiving, board-games, baking
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, drama, musical, thriller, mystery
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, techno, jazz, r&b, classical
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, cricket, water-polo, ice-hockey, sailing
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan of techno##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 7. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is the person watching thriller movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of classical##1
13. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | gardening | baking     | skydiving   | video-games   | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | drama | zombie | thriller | musical        |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | techno      | r&b       | classical       | dubstep       |
| Sport         | cricket | sailing  | ice-hockey    | cycling    | water-polo        |

