.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: cherry, raspberry, blueberry, radish, carrot
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, camping, baking, fishing, video-games
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, disco, gospel, salsa, ambient
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, italian, spanish, french, russian
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 3. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 4. the russian is between the fan of salsa and the person eating radish##2
 5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the right of the spanish##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of disco##1
 9. the fan of ambient is in the middle##1
10. the fan of salsa is the thai##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the thai is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
13. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | carrot  | blueberry     | radish   | raspberry     | cherry |
| Hobby         | video-games | hiking    | baking  | fishing | camping   |
| Music-Genre   | disco        | trance    | ambient     | gospel     | salsa    |
| Nationality   | italian    | spanish | french | russian | thai   |

