.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, water, fanta, tea
There 5 different types of food: tomato, pepper, corn, eggplant, grapefruit
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, musician, teacher, photographer, paramedic
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, ice-hockey, swimming, water-polo, basketball
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the scientist##1
 2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the person drinking water is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the musician##1
 8. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the scientist##1
11. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating corn##1
12. the photographer is on the left of the scientist##1
13. the person eating corn is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | fanta       | tea       | soy-milk   | water      | sprite    |
| Food       | grapefruit | eggplant        | tomato       | corn       | pepper |
| Job        | paramedic     | musician        | photographer | scientist        | teacher  |
| Sport      | water-polo | swimming | tennis      | basketball | ice-hockey  |

