 3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is the nigerian##1
 8. the british is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching action movies is on the right of the dutch##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
11. the person watching western movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who's sport is surfing##2
12. the person drinking cola is on the right of the american##1
13. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1

