The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, train, airplane, car, bus
 1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the train##1
 4. the owner of the snake is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the argentine##2
 5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1
 7. the pakistani is on the right of the dutch##1
 8. the nigerian is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is the pakistani##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the dutch##1
12. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
13. the owner of the snake is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
