 1. the lawyer is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is the lawyer##1
 5. the bartender is in the middle##1
