 7. the software-developer is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is between the owner of the rabbit and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking cola##1
11. the owner of the rat is the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
