 4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the boat is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is chess##2
12. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
13. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | tea       | almond-milk    | coffee | fanta  | water        |
| Hobby       | cooking | singing | chess  | magic-tricks | rock-climbing    |
| Sport       | climbing        | skiing   | snowboarding  | surfing   | skateboarding |
| Transport   | roller       | boat      | taxi      | subway | bike  |

