.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, fanta, juice, lemonade
The people have 5 different jobs:  journalist, police-officer, accountant, nurse, videographer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, horror, family, sports, musical
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, dubstep, techno, pop, reggae
 1. the fan of techno is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 2. the nurse is between the person watching family movies and the accountant##2
 3. the person drinking juice is the nurse##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking juice is between the videographer and the fan of dubstep##2
 7. the fan of pop is the person drinking fanta##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is the fan of techno##1
 9. the fan of folk is on the left of the videographer##1
10. the journalist is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
11. the accountant is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
