.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: triked-games, collecting, filmmaking, board-games, cooking
There are 5 different nationalities: french, russian, italian, turkish, indian
5 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, goat, pony, chinchilla
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, trike, tram, taxi, quad-bike
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the turkish is on the left of the russian##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the bird is between the french and the owner of the ferret##2
 6. the french is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person driving the bike and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is triked-games##2
 9. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's hobby is triked-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is triked-games is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
