.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, singing, country-climbing, puzzles
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, adventure, scientific, romance, disaster
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, salsa, jazz, trance, country
There are 5 different nationalities: spanish, russian, indonesian, colombian, italian
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is between the colombian and the fan of country##2
 3. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of techno##1
 5. the fan of techno is between the italian and the fan of jazz##2
 6. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the fan of trance##1
 8. the person who's hobby is country-climbing is the fan of salsa##1
 9. the spanish is the fan of salsa##1
10. the person who's hobby is country-climbing is on the right of the indonesian##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | singing    | puzzles  | fishing  | drawing      | country-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure    | disaster   | romance | scientific | crime   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | techno    | country    | trance       | salsa         |
| Nationality   | colombian  | russian | italian    | indonesian     | spanish      |

 